(@ENTRY,0,2,"Do you think that demons will play fair? These beasts are more savage than the orcs, more cunning than the undead. Do not attempt to engage Legion by normal standards of war.","<Traduction manquante>",12,0,100,0,0,0,"Marshal Isildor");
